rögtön ez így $(1 - 1)/0$ lenne, tehát $0/0$ tipusu\

- 1. lehetoseg
$ (1 - cos x)/x dot (1 + cos x)/(1 + cos x) = (1 - cos^2x)/x(1 + cos x) = (sin^2 x)/x(1 + cos x) = sin x dot (sin x)/x dot 1/(1 + cos x) $
Ekkor\
$ limits(lim)_(x arrow 0)(sin x dot (sin x)/x dot 1/(1 + cos x)) arrow 0 dot 1 dot 1 = 0 $\

- 2. lehetoseg
$ 1 - cos x = (sin^2 x/2 + cos^2 x/2) - (cos^2 x/2 - sin^2 x/2) = 2sin^2 x/2 $
Ekkor\
$ limits(lim)_(x arrow 0)((2sin^2 x/2)/x) = limits(lim)_(x arrow 0)(sin x/2) dot limits(lim)_(x arrow 0)((sin 2/x)/(x/2)) = 0 dot 1 = 0 $

